# Abyssal Wastelands
*A curated Fallout 4 modlist*

Abyssal Wastelands overhauls the Commonwealth from the ground up — rebuilt settlements and world locations, a deep modern/tactical weapon roster, layered visual and lighting overhauls, and an expanded companion and questing slate — all held together by a robust core framework for stability and compatibility.

---

## 🌍 World & Environment

**Location Overhauls ("After the Fallout" series)** — Concord, Lexington, Salem, Vault 111, Drumlin Diner, Forest Grove Marsh, West Everett, Fah Habah, and the Sacrifice Grounds have all been reworked for greater detail, atmosphere, and post-war storytelling.

**Weathers & Lighting**
- Calamity Weathers (base + Far Harbor, Nuka-World, and interior patches)
- Cyberpunk 2077–inspired neon lighting for Nuka-World and illuminated billboards/posters
- Ultra Exterior Lighting, Enhanced Lights and FX, Light Radius Redux, and targeted lighting passes for the Starlight Drive-In, Red Rocket, and interiors (paired with ELFX-compatible patches)

**Visuals**
- Quantum Horizons ENB (with ENB Helper)
- Clean Water of the Commonwealth, texture and terminal/UI polish (Animated RobCo Logo, TV-accurate RadAway, Better Ammo Boxes, etc.)

---

## 🔫 Weapons

A large modern/tactical arsenal layered onto the vanilla sandbox, including:
- Modern Warfare–inspired weapons: MW2019 M1911, MW Bryson Family (SMG), MW Rytec AMR (Barrett XM109), Tavor X95
- Real-world classics: HK MP5 Complex, Saiga-12 (Soviet Assault Shotgun), FN FAL/SA58, Lee-Enfield No.4 Mk.1, DKS-501 sniper rifle, "The Heavy" WWII machine gun
- Fallout-flavored additions: PBW & Fallout 3–recreation Chinese Assault Rifles, Better Cryolator, F4/76 unique combat shotguns
- Support systems: Scopes Framework, See-Through Scopes, Tactical Reload, Munitions ammo expansion, Leveled Item Fixes, Havok-Aware Bullet-Counted Reload — plus leveled-list and tactical-reload patches to integrate the new weapons into the world

---

## 🛡️ Armor & Power Armor

**Power Armor** — Better Power Armor overhaul (with Nuka-World patch), Institute Power Armor, Hellfire X-03, Enclave X-02, Classic Advanced Power Armor, plus custom Synth and Raider power armor variants.

**Armor & Outfits** — A large CROSS-outfit collection (Chosen of Atom, Brotherhood Recon, Courser Strigidae, Institute Expeditionary Suit, Pre-War Cybernetics, Jetpack), Modern Military Pack (PMC Operators, Tactical Railroad Stalkers, Tactical Minutemen), Saturnite Combat Armor, Forward Operations & Expeditionary Forces packs, NCR Renegade Armor, New Vegas Stealth Suit, Soviet Soldiers gear, and the Vault-Tec/VT Mask MK II.

---

## 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 Body, Face & Hair

Built on CBBE with BodySlide/Outfit Studio, HiPoly Faces REDUX, Extended Facial Sculpting, Eyes of Beauty (Kaleidoscope), an expanded hair library (KS Hairdos, Anto, ANiceOakTree, Lots More Male/Female/Facial hair), plus the Fallout 4 High Heels System and Skeletal Adjustments for CBBE.

