## 🤝 Companions & Quests

**New Companions** — Heather Casdin, KATE, and Synthetic Love, alongside Amazing Follower Tweaks for deeper companion control.

**Quest & Story Additions** — America Rising 2 (Legacy of the Enclave), Project A.R.E.S, Padre Mateo, Vault 28: The Absent Ghoul, Xander's Aid DLC, Old Time Religion, Children of Ug-Qualtoth, Attack of the Lobotomites, and The Bleachers: A Diamond City Story.

---

## ⚙️ Gameplay & Quality of Life

Full Dialogue Interface, Start Me Up Redux (alternate start), Smash to Unlock, Craft Bobby Pins, Carry More with Power Armor REDUX, NPC's Run and Walk at Your Pace, Disable Companion Collision, Skip Kellogg's Memories, Sunshine's Intro Replacer, and Nate's End of the World Supply Chest — plus optional easier hacking/lockpicking and fusion core tweaks for a smoother playthrough.

**UI** — FallUI suite (HUD, Icon Library, Item Sorter) for a cleaner, more modern interface.

---

## 🧩 Core Framework & Stability

RobCo Patcher, Base Object Swapper, Spell Perk Item Distributor, Hydra (with Baka Framework compatibility patch), Community Fixes/Tweaks Merged, Merged RootBehavior, LooksMenu + Customization Compendium, Mod Configuration Menu, Address Library, Addictol Crash Logger, and the Unofficial Fallout 4 Patch (UFO4P) — all running on F4SE with xSE PluginPreloader for reliable startup.

**Base Content** — Includes all Creation Club content (Hellfire Power Armor, Enclave sets, X-02, Heavy Flamer, Halloween, Remnants, Grenade Bundle, Tesla Cannon) and all official DLC (Automatron, Contraptions, Far Harbor, Nuka-World, Vault-Tec Workshop, Wasteland Workshop).

---

*A modlist that blends tactical modern warfare with the Commonwealth's post-apocalyptic soul — heavily visual, combat-focused, and built for long-term stability.*
